ult/hitchhikers/gallery/images/100/zaphod2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A Pattern Beginning to Emerge</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://us.imdb.com/Title?0120591">Armageddon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->, perhaps.<br>
